  • combineBoolArr

    public static boolean[] combineBoolArr(boolean[] arr1,
                                       boolean[] arr2)
    Takes in 2 boolean arrays of length 12. Each index corresponds to a month. It is used to combine bloomtimes
    Parameters:
    arr1 - boolean array of length 12
    arr2 - Another boolean array of length 12
    Returns:
    a boolean array where each index is true if either arr1 or arr2 had true at that same index.

    target - - the string within arr that is being found
